commit.message: remove linux-13 from the list of workflows

CI: bring newer Clang and armhf targets

As for libebml.

Co-authored-by: Rosen Penev <rosenp@gmail.com>

CI: use ninja to build

This makes it easier to read the build logs.

add missing MATROSKA_DLL_API for KaxMatroska

It will still need https://github.com/Matroska-Org/libebml/pull/292 to compile properly on Windows.

disable most verbose warnings in MSVC

They are very noisy and not very useful.

the list of warnings can be found at https://learn.microsoft.com/en-us/cpp/preprocessor/compiler-warnings-that-are-off-by-default

Same as https://github.com/Matroska-Org/libebml/commit/f9af4fd060443d5ebbf615999863d77ced56bdc3

mkvtree: only use libebml/libmatroska API's

replace the ported API's to the actual API's.
add libmatroska2 mkvtree ported to libmatroska

delete unused Makefile

It references a folder that it not there anymore.

don't export EbmlMaster semantic context as a DLL entry

It's accessible via GetContextMaster().
